---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog - Zain Mobarik">
  <!-- Header Section -->
  <header class="mb-16">
    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
        <span class="text-3xl">üìù</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Blog Posts</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-1">
          Thoughts on technology, life, and everything in between.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Blog Posts Grid -->
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
        <time class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
          March 15, 2025
        </time>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">5 min read</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
        <a href="/blog/first-post" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
          Building a Minimalist Personal Website
        </a>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Why I chose to build a simple, content-focused website and the tools I used to create it. Exploring the balance between aesthetics and functionality...
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex space-x-2">
          <span class="text-xs bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Design</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Web Dev</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/first-post" class="text-sm text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-medium">
          Read more ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
        <time class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
          March 10, 2025
        </time>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">8 min read</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
        <a href="/blog/second-post" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
          Lessons from Reading 50 Books This Year
        </a>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        What I learned from committing to reading more and how it changed my perspective on learning, productivity, and personal growth...
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex space-x-2">
          <span class="text-xs bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Learning</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-green-50 text-green-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Books</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/second-post" class="text-sm text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-medium">
          Read more ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
        <time class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
          March 5, 2025
        </time>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">6 min read</span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
        <a href="/blog/third-post" class="hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
          The Power of Small, Consistent Habits
        </a>
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        How making tiny changes compound over time and create meaningful impact in both work and life. A deep dive into habit formation...
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex space-x-2">
          <span class="text-xs bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Habits</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Productivity</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/third-post" class="text-sm text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-medium">
